"html_url": "https://github.com/wasmCloud/weld/pull/149", "diff_url": "https://github.com/wasmCloud/weld/pull/149.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/wasmCloud/weld/pull/149.patch", "merged_at": "2023-04-12T20:09:52Z"}, "body": "## Feature or Problem\r\nForgot to commit this as part of https://github.com/wasmCloud/weld/pull/148, but have already tested with this change\r\n\r\n", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/wasmCloud/weld/issues/149/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/wasmCloud/weld/issues/149/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}, {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/wasmCloud/weld/issues/148", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/wasmCloud/weld", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/wasmCloud/weld/issues/148/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/wasmCloud/weld/issues/148/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/wasmCloud/weld/issues/148/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/wasmCloud/weld/pull/148", "id": 1661529453, "node_id": "PR_kwDOFoi81M5N-Vvy", "number": 148, "title": "Feat/add log level", "user": {"login": "connorsmith256", "id": 3869136, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjM4NjkxMzY=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3869136?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/connorsmith256", "html_url": "https://github.com/connorsmith256", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/connorsmith256/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/connorsmith256/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/connorsmith256/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/connorsmith256/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/connorsmith256/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/connorsmith256/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/connorsmith256/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/connorsmith256/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/connorsmith256/received_events", "type": "User", "user_view_type": "public", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 0, "created_at": "2023-04-10T23:11:41Z", "updated_at": "2023-04-12T19:55:16Z", "closed_at": "2023-04-12T19:55:13Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "type": null, "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/wasmCloud/weld/pulls/148", "html_url": "https://github.com/wasmCloud/weld/pull/148", "diff_url": "https://github.com/wasmCloud/weld/pull/148.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/wasmCloud/weld/pull/148.patch", "merged_at": "2023-04-12T19:55:13Z"}, "body": "## Feature or Problem\r\nThis uses the updated `wasmcloud-core.smithy` from https://github.com/wasmCloud/interfaces/pull/105. Providers will now use the `log_level` field to determine the level filter for logging. Until the host starts passing this value, providers continue to fall back on the `RUST_LOG` environment variable\r\n\r\nThe second commit also refactors the `configure_tracing` logic to be more readable\r\n\r\n## Related Issues\r\nhttps://github.com/wasmCloud/weld/issues/145\r\nhttps://github.com/wasmCloud/interfaces/pull/105\r\n\r\n## Release Information\r\nv0.13.0, since this is a new feature\r\n\r\n## Consumer Impact\r\nN/A. Until the host starts passing this field in `HostData`, providers continue to function as they do today\r\n\r\n## Testing\r\n\r\n### Manual Verification\r\nTested manually with a modified version of the HTTP server provider, updated to use this version of wasmbus-rpc and to log the level received from the host, as well as a test message at the debug level. Results below from starting various hosts with environment variables:\r\n\r\n### Without modification to the host:\r\n\r\nWithout any env vars:\r\n```\r\n2023-04-10T22:47:10.369483Z  INFO httpserver: level: None\r\n```\r\n\r\nWith `RUST_LOG=debug`:\r\n```\r\n2023-04-10T22:46:37.435160Z  INFO httpserver: level: None\r\n2023-04-10T22:46:37.435171Z DEBUG httpserver: debug test\r\n```\r\n\r\n### With the host modified to proxy `WASMCLOUD_STRUCTURED_LOG_LEVEL` as `log_level`:\r\n\r\nWithout any env vars:\r\n```\r\n2023-04-10T22:44:49.448486Z  INFO httpserver: level: Some(\"info\")\r\n```\r\n\r\nWith `RUST_LOG=debug`:\r\n```\r\n2023-04-10T22:43:52.619590Z  INFO httpserver: level: Some(\"info\")\r\n```\r\n\r\nWith `WASMCLOUD_STRUCTURED_LOG_LEVEL=debug`:\r\n```\r\n2023-04-10T22:42:50.249333Z  INFO httpserver: level: Some(\"debug\")\r\n2023-04-10T22:42:50.249341Z DEBUG httpserver: debug teehee\r\n```\r\n\r\nNote that `RUST_LOG` is ignored if `log_level` is set. It's treated as a fallback", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/wasmCloud/weld/issues/148/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/wasmCloud/weld/issues/148/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}]